{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_017pSEhm4K5zVgnhmZJ5eoMo","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All 25 tests pass. The fix:\n\n1. **Positional check**: Only looks at ALL_CAPS candidates at position 1–2 (not all ALL_CAPS in the document), so SKŁADNIKI/WARZYWA at positions 9/25 are ignored.\n2. **Semantic check**: Uses cosine similarity > 0.4 against the pos-0 candidate's embedding to confirm it's a translation, not just any nearby ALL_CAPS.\n3. **Suppression scope**: Uses `startsWith` (not exact match) so multi-line joins like \"PAPRIKA GYERAN-JJIM Ingredients\" are also suppressed along with the detected translation candidate."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":286,"cache_read_input_tokens":40735,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":286},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"522008eb-f4ac-4e97-811e-f5d0ef53d98a","uuid":"36f8c81c-05f6-422d-ab5f-e2bf91037d9d"}
